<br>
Neshma of Vallon Zek sent in an email to report being the first person to obtain an Unholy Steed on a live server.<br>
The horse is black in color and runs extremely fast once it has got going (probably as fast as the 100k~ horses).<br>
<br>
Unlike the store bought horses which have a short delay, the Unholy Steed (and probably the Paladin one) are instant cast.<br>
<br>
Unholy Steeds and Holy Steed are Alternate Advancement rewards for the Shadow Knight and Paladin Class. It requires a minimum of 24 Points to acquire them. <br>
<br>
<br>
Above taken from Casters Realm.<br>
<br>
Hmm, seems like not such a good investment of hard earned skill points if the only advantage our horse has is the instant click effect, which hell we can get with jboots if we are really in such a hurry to get going. /sigh so much for hoping for something special. (yes you save 100k thats all)<br>
